# Omarchy / Hyprland packages for omarchy-bootc
# One package name per line.  Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
# Installed by build/20-omarchy.sh using pacman.
#
# This file is intentionally left as a placeholder for the first working VM
# image.  Uncomment packages as you validate them in the build.
# All packages must be available in the official Arch repos (or AUR via a
# custom AUR helper layer added to the Containerfile).

# ── Wayland / Hyprland compositor ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# hyprland
# xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland
# wayland
# wl-clipboard
# xdg-utils

# ── Status bar & launcher ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# waybar
# wofi
# rofi-wayland

# ── Notifications ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# mako

# ── Screenshot / screen lock ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# grim
# slurp
# swaylock

# ── Terminal emulator ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# alacritty
# kitty

# ── File manager ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# thunar

# ── Theming — Catppuccin Mocha (matches Omarchy defaults) ────────────────────
# catppuccin-gtk-theme-mocha    (AUR)
# papirus-icon-theme

# ── Fonts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ttf-nerd-fonts-symbols
# noto-fonts
# noto-fonts-emoji

# ── Omarchy tooling ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (add project-specific packages here — e.g. from omarchy's package list)
